==History==
Ostensibly an agency dedicated to helping [[children]], it actually, is the only place where these societal derelicts can exercise any powar. Unfortunately, said powar is not exercised over the rightful objects of their wrath, rather, it is exercised only on Caucasians who cannot afford [[lawyer]]s. The actual level of services to children is marginal at best, usually consisting of experimenting with various types of [[drugs|medication]] to keep them relatively subdued, "gently" coercing the child in question to begin to agree with their claims against the parents or removing children from an "alleged" abusive home environment and putting them in an ''actual'' abusive foster home environment.

