=="Helping" the community==
Child Welfare agencies have a unique knack for not noticing, or ignoring children in actual danger, especially children from [[nigra|minority groups]]. These children usually endure rather grisly torture, and assured an [http://archive.recordonline.com/archive/2003/10/08/pbpettwa.htm early death]. However, they manage to come calling at your door when your child falls and ends up with a bruise. Fuck, it doesn't even take ''that'' anymore. You don't even have to lay a glove on the kid. Just yelling at your spouse will bring these social services sharks out better than a barrel of fresh chum off the coast of [[Australia|Ausfailia]].

Once they arrive with your [[nazi|friendly]] members of law enforcement, they can then, ''without a search warrant'', regardless of the apparent health or happiness of the child, demand entry under "probable cause". They will then set the cops to hem in the parents in a secluded area, while they proceed through your entire home, and [[lie|"speak"]] to the child in question. Alone.

The parents then get confronted about, not the ''good'' aspects of the home life and environment for the child in question, but about any fucking nit-picking thing that this valiant "defender" of children everywhere has found. It's after this that the "help" really comes rolling in...

If the parents are lucky the child isn't removed, but you had better believe that there are gonna be some changes made, buster! Anything sharper in your home than a spork? Get rid of it. You have a liquor cabinet of ''any'' kind? You're a lush! Dump it. Yes, even the Glenfiddich you've had, unopened, for the last 20 years.

These and more are leveled at the parents who, by now, are scratching their fucking [[WTF|heads in total bewilderment]].

Being [[IRL]] cowards, Child Welfare Workers also avoid the intarwebs, due to the likely fact, that if the right disgruntled individual managed to find them, they would likely regret it. Many agencies run obsolete [[Windows]] systems due to "budget constraints", however there is the counterpoint that they often get paid far too fucking much government cheese for their jobs. They bitch constantly about budget cuts, but they have no problem driving that new Beemer to and from the office.
