Being cowards, largely populated by liberals and given their lack of service to minorities, strongly indicates that they are [[racist]], as well. They are afraid that they will come to harm at the hands of enraged Negroes or Mexicans, so they assiduously avoid them. many are [[Jews]], so anyone who looks like a [[skinhead]] is avoided, as well.

Interestingly enough the "new breed" of this [[whore|worker]] emerging of late tend to be a yuppified, early to mid 20's [[cunt|bitch]] who, although she will claim altruism and doing her job "[[lie|for the best interests of the family and child]]", she is [[lesbian|unmarried]] and,naturally, has no children of her own.

